7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Character.ai and Jasper Chat share a solid foundation of core features including Memory, Multilingual. Where Character.ai pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Voice Input, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Jasper Chat uniquely offers File Upload and Api Access, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Character.ai holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Jasper Chat scores 6/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Character.ai offers a more budget-friendly entry point at Free, compared to Jasper Chat's starting price of $49/mo. Character.ai has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Jasper Chat does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
